Package: pybit-svn
Architecture: all
Depends: curl, ${misc:Depends}
Description: subversion post commit hook for pybit
 Subversion post commit hook to check for interesting
 changes in the repository and post a directory back to
 the controller using curl.

Package: pybit-controller
Architecture: all
Depends: pybit-common,
 ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: buildd controller for pybit

Package: pybit-client
Architecture: all
Depends: python-amqplib, python-debian, sbuild,
 pybit-common,
 ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: buildd client support for pybit
 This package provides the python client for pybit
 to build packages using sbuild.

Package: pybit-web
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: pybit web frontend

Package: pybit-common
Architecture: all
Depends: ${python:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Common objects for pybit
 Contains object definitions to common
 python objects between pybit services.
